{
  "title": "Mildly Seasoned Filipino Pork Belly Noodles",
  "description": "A floral and tender Filipino dish featuring pork belly slices and noodles, perfect for a monsoon day, this dairy-free-friendly meal is sure to satisfy your cravings.",
  "cuisine": "Filipino",
  "diet": [
    "dairy-free"
